<h3>Common Mistakes That Kill Results</h3>
<p><strong>Don't automate everything immediately</strong> - Start with one tool, master it, then add more. Customers can tell when content feels robotic.</p>
<p><strong>Don't ignore negative reviews</strong> - AI can draft responses, but authentic handling of criticism builds more trust than generic replies.</p>
<p><strong>Don't set and forget</strong> - AI tools need monthly optimization based on performance data.</p>
<p><strong>Don't skip the local connection</strong> - Generic AI content doesn't work. Always add area-specific references and genuine local knowledge.</p>
<p><strong>Don't expect overnight results</strong> - Local SEO improvements typically show measurable results in 30-60 days, with significant gains in 90 days.</p>
